---
title: Peanut Sweet Potato Stew with Seared Halloumi and Fresh Cilantro
description: You don't need a blender for this no-fuss West African sweet potato and peanut stew. Topped with seared halloumi, cilantro and roasted peanuts, it's a hearty meal you won't soon forget!
